oc:kn_4300da8d a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When starting a new investment memo engagement" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Request all available data upfront (financials, market analysis, management assessment, comparable deals) for more complete memos. More context yields better analysis." ;
    oc:hasRationale "The quality of the memo is directly proportional to the quality and completeness of the input data" ;
    oc:severityLevel "LOW" .

oc:kn_9c3b312f a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Standard ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When selecting memo format based on deal type" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Adapt memo structure to investment type: use the 9-section VC template for venture deals, 12-section PE template for buyouts, or abbreviated formats (Deal Summary, Quick Take, Follow-on) as appropriate." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Different investment contexts require different analytical depth and section emphasis" ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_a68c8e13 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When drafting the Risk Analysis section" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Every risk in the risk analysis section should have a corresponding mitigant. Use the likelihood/impact matrix (H/M/L) for systematic risk assessment." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Unmitigated risks undermine the credibility of the investment recommendation and leave the IC without a balanced view" ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_e3021dce a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating or sharing any memo output" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Do not present the memo output as investment advice or a recommendation to any external party. Always mark as confidential internal document." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Investment memos are internal decision-support documents; external distribution creates legal and compliance risk" ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_e9f00593 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Always — this skill is a document drafting tool, not an investment advisor" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Cannot conduct primary due diligence, provide investment advice, access proprietary deal data, or replace professional investment judgment. Analysis is based solely on provided information." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Investment decisions require human judgment, proprietary data, and regulatory compliance that this skill cannot provide" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

